1
00:01:47,291 --> 00:01:48,958
[MOMO]
Wait a minute! Hold on!

2
00:01:49,041 --> 00:01:51,666
Don't pull me like this.
You're hurting my hand.

3
00:01:54,250 --> 00:01:57,458
[MOMO] This is where I saw
Toji and Sae kissing.

4
00:01:57,541 --> 00:01:59,250
Why did he bring me here?

5
00:02:03,125 --> 00:02:04,666
[MOMO]
What's this all about?

6
00:02:04,750 --> 00:02:05,708
[MOMO gasps]

7
00:02:09,125 --> 00:02:10,083
[MOMO]
No!

8
00:02:28,208 --> 00:02:29,333
[SAE]
He must have assumed

9
00:02:29,416 --> 00:02:31,416
that getting a kiss
from you would be easy.

10
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:38,291
[MOMO]
What just happened?

11
00:02:41,583 --> 00:02:42,791
What's up, Toji?

12
00:02:42,875 --> 00:02:44,083
Will you give this to Momo?

13
00:02:44,166 --> 00:02:45,333
Uh...

14
00:02:47,625 --> 00:02:48,500
Toji!

15
00:02:48,583 --> 00:02:49,666
How's it going?

16
00:02:50,875 --> 00:02:52,583
No one ignores me!

17
00:02:52,666 --> 00:02:54,458
Toji! Why are you running?!

18
00:02:55,333 --> 00:02:56,416
[TOJI gasps]

19
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,666
What's going on?
You totally blew me off.

20
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,041
Where's Momo?

21
00:03:00,125 --> 00:03:01,041
[TOJI panting]

22
00:03:01,125 --> 00:03:02,041
It's no good.

23
00:03:02,125 --> 00:03:03,291
[SAE]
Huh?

24
00:03:03,375 --> 00:03:04,916
I screwed everything up.

25
00:03:05,833 --> 00:03:07,583
Momo hates me.

26
00:03:07,666 --> 00:03:08,958
I know she does.

27
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:15,833
[cars honking]

28
00:03:15,916 --> 00:03:18,625
[bus honking]

29
00:03:18,708 --> 00:03:19,833
[KAIRI]
Watch out!

30
00:03:24,541 --> 00:03:26,458
You almost got
yourself killed, Momo.

31
00:03:26,541 --> 00:03:30,125
Yeah, thanks...
I'm aware of that.

32
00:03:30,208 --> 00:03:30,833
[brakes squeal]

33
00:03:30,916 --> 00:03:33,000
[KAIRI grunts]

34
00:03:33,083 --> 00:03:34,916
See what I mean?

35
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,291
I better walk you home.

36
00:03:36,375 --> 00:03:38,083
[MOMO] Don't bother.
I can get home myself.

37
00:03:38,166 --> 00:03:39,333
[KAIRI]
So you claim,

38
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:41,416
but who was it that just
got smacked by a bicycle

39
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:45,541
and nearly flattened into a
pancake by oncoming traffic?

40
00:03:45,625 --> 00:03:47,458
[MOMO growls]

41
00:03:47,541 --> 00:03:51,041
What's with you today? Is it so
bad that Toji tried to kiss you?

42
00:03:52,583 --> 00:03:54,166
Man, I don't get you.

43
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:56,000
I thought if the guy
you loved tried to kiss you

44
00:03:56,083 --> 00:03:57,583
--you'd be happy about it.
--What's not to get?

45
00:03:57,666 --> 00:04:00,000
He tried to kiss me in the same
place he made out with Sae.

46
00:04:00,083 --> 00:04:01,833
I know that. So what?

47
00:04:01,916 --> 00:04:03,291
[MOMO]
It's just wrong.

48
00:04:03,375 --> 00:04:05,875
I would never kiss him in
the same spot he kissed her.

49
00:04:05,958 --> 00:04:08,125
I can't believe Toji
would do such a thing!

50
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:10,083
Forcing me into the garden...

51
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:13,291
...without even bothering
to ask how I felt about it.

52
00:04:13,375 --> 00:04:17,250
That puts him on the same
idiotic level as you, Kairi!

53
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:18,291
[KAIRI grunts]

54
00:04:23,083 --> 00:04:25,333
[MOMO] He was like
a different person...

55
00:04:25,416 --> 00:04:27,875
I guess he is only judging me
by my appearance after all,

56
00:04:27,958 --> 00:04:29,916
even if he said it wasn't true.

57
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,416
He probably thinks
I'm some slut.

58
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,250
It just isn't fair.

59
00:04:34,333 --> 00:04:34,875
[KAIRI]
You love him, right?

60
00:04:34,958 --> 00:04:36,250
[MOMO gasps]

61
00:04:36,333 --> 00:04:37,458
Then just tell him

62
00:04:37,541 --> 00:04:40,208
that this idea that
you're a slut is wrong.

63
00:04:40,291 --> 00:04:42,833
What's most important here
are your feelings, not his.

64
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:44,291
[MOMO]
Yeah, but...

65
00:04:44,375 --> 00:04:46,125
This is true for all men.

66
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:48,875
We often have ulterior
motives with girls.

67
00:04:48,958 --> 00:04:50,208
If you don't like that,

68
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:51,708
then be clear with him
and tell him how you feel.

69
00:04:51,791 --> 00:04:54,125
And if he decides to leave
you for something that trivial,

70
00:04:54,208 --> 00:04:56,166
then he wasn't worth
your time anyway.

71
00:05:02,416 --> 00:05:05,750
[KAIRI] What's most important
here are your feelings, not his.

72
00:05:05,833 --> 00:05:07,125
[MOMO]
I never expected Kairi

73
00:05:07,208 --> 00:05:09,750
of all people to be
filled with such insight.

74
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:13,750
But I guess he was trying
to make me feel better.

75
00:05:13,833 --> 00:05:15,500
[dog barking]

76
00:05:15,583 --> 00:05:18,708
I'm thinking here, stupid dog.

77
00:05:18,791 --> 00:05:21,458
[MOMO] Actually, regardless of
what's happened in the past,

78
00:05:21,541 --> 00:05:23,333
he's really taught
me quite a bit.

79
00:05:24,458 --> 00:05:26,375
[MOMO] I mean, if he hadn't
been there for me today,

80
00:05:26,458 --> 00:05:28,291
I'd probably be
a complete wreck by now.

81
00:05:28,375 --> 00:05:29,333
[water splashing]

82
00:05:30,958 --> 00:05:33,500
[MOMO] Maybe it wouldn't be such
a bad idea to give Kairi a shot.

83
00:05:35,125 --> 00:05:36,000
[MOMO]
We'll see.

84
00:05:36,083 --> 00:05:37,500
[KAIRI]
You love him, right?

85
00:05:37,583 --> 00:05:38,791
Then just tell him
that this idea

86
00:05:38,875 --> 00:05:40,375
that you're a slut is wrong.

87
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:43,208
[MOMO] But I don't wanna have to
convince him of who I really am.

88
00:05:44,791 --> 00:05:45,875
Oh, Toji...

89
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:46,916
[dog barking]

90
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:49,250
Would you shut up?!

91
00:05:49,333 --> 00:05:51,000
Uh...

92
00:05:51,083 --> 00:05:52,541
[TOJI gasps]

93
00:05:52,625 --> 00:05:53,791
[MOMO gasps]

94
00:05:53,875 --> 00:05:57,291
Why? Why? Why? Why is
Toji outside my house?!

95
00:06:02,625 --> 00:06:04,666
How long have you been here?

96
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,000
Not long.

97
00:06:06,083 --> 00:06:08,125
I happened to be walking
through the neighborhood.

98
00:06:09,416 --> 00:06:10,625
[MOMO]
Liar.

99
00:06:10,708 --> 00:06:12,625
He's still in
his school uniform.

100
00:06:12,708 --> 00:06:15,083
He hasn't even been home yet.

101
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:16,541
Look, I'm...

102
00:06:16,625 --> 00:06:18,416
I'm sorry.

103
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,583
When I saw you talking
to Kairi by the pool,

104
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,458
I completely lost it.

105
00:06:22,541 --> 00:06:24,375
It looked like you were
laughing and I thought that

106
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:27,541
maybe you have more fun
with him than with me.

107
00:06:27,625 --> 00:06:29,500
I saw you two together
and I just kept thinking,

108
00:06:29,583 --> 00:06:31,875
"Hey! Get away
from my girlfriend!"

109
00:06:31,958 --> 00:06:33,041
And...

110
00:06:33,125 --> 00:06:35,041
I lost my temper.

111
00:06:35,125 --> 00:06:37,208
[MOMO] He came all the way
to my house at this hour

112
00:06:37,291 --> 00:06:38,750
just to tell me that?

113
00:06:42,291 --> 00:06:44,208
I'm glad.

114
00:06:44,291 --> 00:06:45,291
I was afraid you'd tell me

115
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:47,291
to get lost before
I could say that.

116
00:06:47,375 --> 00:06:48,791
[MOMO]
I was wrong!

117
00:06:48,875 --> 00:06:51,333
Toji isn't going out with me
because he thinks I'm easy.

118
00:06:51,416 --> 00:06:53,875
He really cares
about my feelings.

119
00:06:53,958 --> 00:06:57,166
But even if he did
want that... then maybe.

120
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:58,416
[TOJI gasps]

121
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,958
[MOMO]
Maybe...

122
00:07:00,041 --> 00:07:00,875
[MOMO gasps]

123
00:07:00,958 --> 00:07:02,458
[MOMO]
Ahh! What am I doing?!

124
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:04,750
I shouldn't be
thinking about that!

125
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:08,041
[TOJI]
Well, I'd better get home.

126
00:07:08,125 --> 00:07:09,708
[MOMO] Wait. I'll walk
you to the corner.

127
00:07:09,791 --> 00:07:11,583
[TOJI]
That's okay. It's pretty late.

128
00:07:11,666 --> 00:07:13,208
I'll just see you tomorrow.

129
00:07:13,291 --> 00:07:14,500
[MOMO]
Sounds good.

130
00:07:20,791 --> 00:07:24,500
What a relief. Uh...?

131
00:07:24,583 --> 00:07:26,750
Toji!

132
00:07:26,833 --> 00:07:27,958
I took this out of your wallet

133
00:07:28,041 --> 00:07:29,708
the other day
without telling you.

134
00:07:29,791 --> 00:07:31,250
When I saw it there,
I was shocked.

135
00:07:31,333 --> 00:07:33,500
But I'm sure you have a
reasonable explanation for it.

136
00:07:33,583 --> 00:07:36,000
I'm sorry I kept it from you.
Will you please forgive me?

137
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:37,500
Uh, what?

138
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:40,500
It's okay. You don't have
to say anything. I trust you.

139
00:07:40,583 --> 00:07:42,041
[MOMO]
Exactly.

140
00:07:42,125 --> 00:07:45,166
What's most important is that
Toji and I love each other.

141
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:46,625
See ya tomorrow.

142
00:07:55,708 --> 00:07:58,750
[STUDENTS chatter]

143
00:07:58,833 --> 00:08:00,541
What is this thing anyway?

144
00:08:01,583 --> 00:08:02,541
[TOJI]
Hm?

145
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,875
[TOJI]
Morning, Sae.

146
00:08:05,958 --> 00:08:07,166
Hey...

147
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,875
Does this thing belong to you?

148
00:08:11,708 --> 00:08:13,875
Uhh... You're crying!

149
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,833
I didn't notice... Are you okay?

150
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:17,833
No, I'm not...

151
00:08:17,916 --> 00:08:18,958
Momo's mad at me.

152
00:08:19,041 --> 00:08:20,041
She is?

153
00:08:20,125 --> 00:08:22,000
She must have
been watching us...

154
00:08:22,083 --> 00:08:23,541
...when we kissed in the garden.

155
00:08:23,625 --> 00:08:25,083
[TOJI gasps]

156
00:08:25,166 --> 00:08:28,000
What should I do?
I was only trying to help her

157
00:08:28,083 --> 00:08:30,000
--and now I've made her mad.
--[TOJI whimpers]

158
00:08:30,083 --> 00:08:33,708
[SAE cries]

159
00:08:33,791 --> 00:08:35,791
Wow... Sorry.

160
00:08:35,875 --> 00:08:40,833
[SAE cries]

161
00:08:40,916 --> 00:08:44,208
[MOMO]
Sae... You never quit!

162
00:08:44,291 --> 00:08:44,750
[MOMO]
Toji.

163
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:46,166
[SAE, TOJI gasp]

164
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:48,333
--[MOMO] I need to talk to you!
--[TOJI] What... Hey!

165
00:08:48,416 --> 00:08:49,583
[TOJI grunts]

166
00:08:49,666 --> 00:08:50,958
[MOMO] I don't want you
talking to Sae anymore.

167
00:08:51,041 --> 00:08:52,166
What was she saying?

168
00:08:52,250 --> 00:08:53,583
She's probably bad-mouthing
me again, right?

169
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:55,458
Look, I don't know what she's
been telling you lately,

170
00:08:55,541 --> 00:08:57,000
but don't believe
a word she says.

171
00:08:57,083 --> 00:08:58,791
Pretty much everything that
comes out of that girl's mouth

172
00:08:58,875 --> 00:09:00,333
is a manipulative lie.

173
00:09:00,416 --> 00:09:01,916
So even if she comes up
to you in the hall

174
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:04,625
and starts talking,
just ignore her. 'Kay?

175
00:09:04,708 --> 00:09:06,625
Why would I do that?

176
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:08,000
She's your friend, right?

177
00:09:08,083 --> 00:09:11,000
Her my friend? Yeah, that's
what I used to believe.

178
00:09:12,375 --> 00:09:13,958
This will sound weird
but I've been meaning

179
00:09:14,041 --> 00:09:16,250
to ask you for awhile.

180
00:09:16,333 --> 00:09:17,916
You and Sae haven't been
going out on dates

181
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,708
--behind my back, have you?
-[TOJI gasps]

182
00:09:19,791 --> 00:09:21,416
But... Momo, I'm with you.

183
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:24,166
Why would I be seeing Sae?
That doesn't make any sense.

184
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,000
[SAE]
She must have been watching us

185
00:09:26,083 --> 00:09:27,250
when we kissed in the garden.

186
00:09:27,333 --> 00:09:29,541
[TOJI]
So Momo did see us kiss.

187
00:09:29,625 --> 00:09:32,291
That explains why
she ran off yesterday.

188
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:35,000
She must be
really angry with me.

189
00:09:35,083 --> 00:09:37,333
Momo, why would you ask
me something like that?

190
00:09:37,416 --> 00:09:38,708
Uh...

191
00:09:38,791 --> 00:09:40,208
[MOMO]
I knew it!

192
00:09:40,291 --> 00:09:42,416
Everything she's said so far
has been nothing but a lie!

193
00:09:44,416 --> 00:09:48,083
[MOMO] Nevermind. It was a
stupid question. Forget it.

194
00:09:48,166 --> 00:09:49,000
Yeah, sure.

195
00:09:49,083 --> 00:09:56,333
[bell ringing]

196
00:09:56,416 --> 00:09:57,375
[MOMO gasps]

197
00:09:58,833 --> 00:10:01,791
So, Toji paid a visit to
your house late last night, huh?

198
00:10:01,875 --> 00:10:03,291
How do you know that?

199
00:10:03,375 --> 00:10:04,583
Because I was the one

200
00:10:04,666 --> 00:10:06,041
who told him to visit you
in the first place.

201
00:10:06,125 --> 00:10:07,166
[MOMO gasps]

202
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:09,000
[SAE snickers]

203
00:10:09,083 --> 00:10:10,125
What's all this nonsense

204
00:10:10,208 --> 00:10:12,083
about you not allowing
him to kiss you?

205
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:15,583
He told me everything
'cause we're close like that.

206
00:10:15,666 --> 00:10:17,041
[MOMO]
No way.

207
00:10:17,125 --> 00:10:19,375
Toji was so blown away at
the fact that you denied him

208
00:10:19,458 --> 00:10:21,458
that he got depressed.
That's when I stepped in

209
00:10:21,541 --> 00:10:24,750
and gave him the advice to go to
your house and make up with you.

210
00:10:24,833 --> 00:10:26,541
You know, when it comes to Toji,

211
00:10:26,625 --> 00:10:28,458
I've always been
there by his side.

212
00:10:28,541 --> 00:10:29,541
Plus, he'll do practically...

213
00:10:29,625 --> 00:10:31,166
[MOMO]
No. Don't let her get to you.

214
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:33,416
If you start accusing Toji
of dating Sae again,

215
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:37,250
then he'll distance himself,
which is exactly what she wants.

216
00:10:38,583 --> 00:10:40,750
You should hope you get
another chance to kiss him

217
00:10:40,833 --> 00:10:42,375
because his lips are way soft.

218
00:10:42,458 --> 00:10:43,916
Get outta my way! I can't clean!

219
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,041
[SAE gasps, yelps]

220
00:10:45,125 --> 00:10:46,458
[ALL gasps]

221
00:10:46,541 --> 00:10:47,958
[TOJI gasps]

222
00:10:48,041 --> 00:10:57,083
[STUDENTS murmuring]

223
00:10:57,166 --> 00:10:59,875
[MOMO] What happened?
I barely touched her.

224
00:10:59,958 --> 00:11:01,000
[TOJI]
Sae!

225
00:11:01,083 --> 00:11:02,125
Hey, are you alright?

226
00:11:02,208 --> 00:11:03,125
Look she's hurt!

227
00:11:03,208 --> 00:11:04,500
Can you stand up?

228
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:07,375
[SAE whimpers]

229
00:11:07,458 --> 00:11:10,041
I didn't... mean to...

230
00:11:10,125 --> 00:11:12,041
Let's hope she
didn't break something.

231
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,750
[MOMO]
Great.

232
00:11:35,833 --> 00:11:37,916
Now everyone's looking at
me like I'm the bad guy.

233
00:11:44,708 --> 00:11:47,875
Sae, did that bruise on
your cheek come from...

234
00:11:47,958 --> 00:11:50,333
[MOMO] I don't want you
talking to Sae anymore.

235
00:11:50,416 --> 00:11:52,125
Uh... Just nevermind.

236
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:02,250
[MOMO gasps]

237
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:07,000
You lousy faker!

238
00:12:07,083 --> 00:12:09,041
Sae! Wait for me!

239
00:12:09,125 --> 00:12:10,083
Momo?

240
00:12:10,166 --> 00:12:11,166
--[MOMO grunts]
--[SAE yelps]

241
00:12:11,250 --> 00:12:12,916
Just as I thought!
Your leg is fine!

242
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,791
You're not injured
at all, ya big faker!

243
00:12:14,875 --> 00:12:16,208
You made a big show
of falling down

244
00:12:16,291 --> 00:12:17,416
in front of Toji, didn't you?

245
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,291
What's with you?
You're scaring me!

246
00:12:19,375 --> 00:12:21,916
You never seem to get it!
Stay away from Toji!

247
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,125
Momo, stop this.

248
00:12:23,208 --> 00:12:24,708
Do not buy into her crap.

249
00:12:24,791 --> 00:12:26,666
She'll do anything to get her
hands on what she wants,

250
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:29,458
even if that means lying and
deceiving her so-called friends

251
00:12:29,541 --> 00:12:33,000
Momo, please! Do you really
believe I would do that to you?

252
00:12:33,083 --> 00:12:34,416
[MOMO]
Knock it off, Sae!

253
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,541
