to copy what everyone else does!

257
00:12:43,541 --> 00:12:44,416
[SAE gasps]

258
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,250
When have I ever copied someone?

259
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:47,375
Every day.

260
00:12:47,458 --> 00:12:48,458
[SAE]
That's not true!

261
00:12:48,541 --> 00:12:49,375
[MOMO]
Yes, it is!

262
00:12:49,458 --> 00:12:50,583
[SAE]
No, it isn't!

263
00:12:50,666 --> 00:12:51,458
--[MOMO] You know it's true!
--[TOJI growls]

264
00:12:51,541 --> 00:12:52,916
[SAE]
You're such a liar!

265
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,583
[TOJI]
That's enough!

266
00:12:54,666 --> 00:12:55,791
[MOMO gasps]

267
00:12:55,875 --> 00:12:57,333
[MOMO]
Toji?

268
00:12:57,416 --> 00:13:00,875
Look, Momo, I understand you're
angry because I kissed Sae.

269
00:13:00,958 --> 00:13:03,625
Well, she's not the only one
you should be angry with.

270
00:13:03,708 --> 00:13:06,541
But... She's a liar.
Don't stand up for her.

271
00:13:06,625 --> 00:13:09,125
I dunno what's up with you
two, but the last few days,

272
00:13:09,208 --> 00:13:11,333
Sae's done nothing
but look out for you.

273
00:13:11,416 --> 00:13:13,625
Yet, for some reason,
you can't see that.

274
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:16,041
It makes me think that maybe...

275
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:17,791
