276
00:13:17,875 --> 00:13:18,916
[MOMO gasps]

277
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:26,958
[SAE]
Meow.

278
00:13:29,375 --> 00:13:30,750
[MOMO]
You're a jerk, Toji!

279
00:13:30,833 --> 00:13:32,750
I'm sick of you
believing Sae over me

280
00:13:32,833 --> 00:13:34,500
