looking like a selfish,

287
00:13:49,791 --> 00:13:51,375
jealous, violent girl.

288
00:13:56,166 --> 00:13:58,458
[TOJI] Mom. Do we have
anything for a stomachache?

289
00:13:58,541 --> 00:13:59,458
[TOJI'S MOM]
Oh... I'm sorry

290
00:13:59,541 --> 00:14:00,666
you're not feeling
well, sweetie.

291
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:03,583
We should have some
medicine in the drawer.

292
00:14:03,666 --> 00:14:04,791
[phone rings]

293
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:08,583
[TOJI'S MOM]
Hello? Oh, yes, hi.

294
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:10,125
Of course. Let me get him.

295
00:14:10,208 --> 00:14:12,541
Toji, phone's for you.
It's Momo.

296
00:14:13,666 --> 00:14:15,083
[TOJI]
Hello?

297
00:14:15,166 --> 00:14:18,416
[MOMO] Oh crap. He sounds
like he's in a terrible mood.

298
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:21,125
I've got to do this though.

299
00:14:21,208 --> 00:14:23,916
Uh, hi, Toji... I wanted
to say I'm sorry...

300
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,041
About what happened earlier.

301
00:14:26,125 --> 00:14:27,625
[TOJI grunts]

302
00:14:27,708 --> 00:14:30,375
[TOJI]
Uh-huh.

303
00:14:30,458 --> 00:14:31,916
