Momo.

314
00:14:52,666 --> 00:14:53,458
[MOMO]
Yeah?

315
00:14:53,541 --> 00:14:54,458
Look I don't mean to be rude,

316
00:14:54,541 --> 00:14:55,750
but I'm not in
the mood right now

317
00:14:55,833 --> 00:14:57,375
to listen to you
bad-mouth Sae, okay?

318
00:14:57,458 --> 00:14:59,250
[MOMO] I know it may sound
like I'm bad-mouthing her,

319
00:14:59,333 --> 00:15:00,916
but please just hear me out.

320
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,500
She's a lot more calculating
that you give her credit for.

321
00:15:03,583 --> 00:15:05,291
[TOJI]
I apologize for kissing Sae.

322
00:15:05,375 --> 00:15:07,541
It was stupid and
I shouldn't have done it.

323
00:15:07,625 --> 00:15:10,125
If I were in your place,
I'd feel the same way.

324
00:15:10,208 --> 00:15:12,083
You got every reason
to be mad at me.

325
00:15:12,166 --> 00:15:13,250
But I'm not.

326
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:15,541
I'm... I'm sorry for
the mistake I made.

327
00:15:15,625 --> 00:15:16,958
I never meant to betray you.

328
00:15:17,041 --> 00:15:18,458
You haven't betrayed me...

329
00:15:18,541 --> 00:15:21,291
You have to believe me, I'm not
that angry about the kiss.

330
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:23,458
Well, I guess I can't say
I'm totally fine with it.

331
00:15:23,541 --> 00:15:24,916
But what I'm trying
to say is that--

332
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:25,791
[TOJI]
I gotta go.

333
00:15:25,875 --> 00:15:27,208
Toji? Toji!

334
00:15:27,291 --> 00:15:29,708
[phone beeps]

335
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:46,333
[HOMEROOM TEACHER] Toji and
Momo are both absent today.

336
00:15:46,416 --> 00:15:48,500
We got a call from Toji's
parents this morning.

337
00:15:48,583 --> 00:15:49,666
Last night he was suffering

338
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:51,458
from what he thought
was a stomachache.

339
00:15:51,541 --> 00:15:54,625
It turns out it was appendicitis
so he's in the hospital now.

340
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:57,291
[HOMEROOM TEACHER] If anyone
would like to volunteer

341
00:15:57,375 --> 00:15:59,583
to take him class notes and
a study guide for the final,

342
00:15:59,666 --> 00:16:01,250
I'm sure he'll appreciate it.

343
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:05,333
[GIRL C] This was my
third trip to the zoo this year

344
00:16:05,416 --> 00:16:06,666
