346
00:16:07,875 --> 00:16:08,791
[BOY A]
What's this?

347
00:16:08,875 --> 00:16:10,375
[GIRL D]
It's a note for everyone.

348
00:16:10,458 --> 00:16:12,333
[GIRL E] Read it then pass
it on. Keep it a secret.

349
00:16:12,416 --> 00:16:15,208
[GIRL F] Oh, we are
so evil. Ha-ha-ha.

350
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:17,083
[STUDENTS whispering]

351
00:16:17,166 --> 00:16:19,583
[MOMO panting]

352
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:23,750
[MOMO] I can't believe I
overslept! Ugh, I hate this!

353
00:16:29,041 --> 00:16:30,500
What's going on?

354
00:16:38,166 --> 00:16:40,000
[MOMO] Why's everyone
acting so weird?

355
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:43,083
[MOMO]
He's absent today?

356
00:16:44,541 --> 00:16:45,875
[MOMO sighs]

357
00:16:45,958 --> 00:16:47,791
[MOMO] I'm not sure if I'm
disappointed or relieved.

358
00:16:47,875 --> 00:16:49,375
[HISTORY TEACHER]
When you take those factors

359
00:16:49,458 --> 00:16:53,125
into consideration, it's quite
obvious why Buddhism began...

360
00:16:53,208 --> 00:16:55,041
[MOMO] I wonder what's
wrong with him?

361
00:16:59,041 --> 00:17:00,416
[GIRL E]
What a slut!

362
00:17:02,125 --> 00:17:05,000
