like, ten guys last summer.

363
00:17:05,083 --> 00:17:06,791
[GIRL E]
Yeah, she's a tramp.

364
00:17:10,458 --> 00:17:12,083
[MOMO] How dare they
talk about me like that!

365
00:17:12,166 --> 00:17:14,458
They don't even know me!

366
00:17:14,541 --> 00:17:17,166
[SAE]
Hello? Toji?

367
00:17:17,250 --> 00:17:18,375
How are we feeling?

368
00:17:18,458 --> 00:17:20,375
Oh, hey there, Sae.

369
00:17:20,458 --> 00:17:21,500
[SAE]
You poor thing.

370
00:17:21,583 --> 00:17:23,791
I can't believe you
had appendicitis.

371
00:17:23,875 --> 00:17:25,458
So the surgery went well?

372
00:17:25,541 --> 00:17:27,041
[TOJI]
Hmm.

373
00:17:27,125 --> 00:17:28,750
I got you these flowers, well,
they're from the whole class.

374
00:17:28,833 --> 00:17:30,125
Oh, and here are some notes.

375
00:17:31,625 --> 00:17:34,125
So, at what point did your
stomach start hurting?

376
00:17:34,208 --> 00:17:35,958
Last I saw,
you looked fine to me.

377
00:17:36,041 --> 00:17:38,500
