right before dinner...

378
00:17:39,458 --> 00:17:40,416
--Sae...
--[SAE gasps]

379
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:41,916
Are you here by yourself?

380
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,333
Uh... yeah, I...

381
00:17:43,416 --> 00:17:45,500
I invited Momo but
I guess she didn't...

382
00:17:47,083 --> 00:17:48,458
I see.

383
00:17:50,791 --> 00:17:53,166
[SAE] Well, I better get going.
I hope you feel better.

384
00:17:53,250 --> 00:17:54,791
[TOJI]
Huh? So soon?

385
00:17:54,875 --> 00:17:56,166
[SAE]
If I stay here any longer,

386
00:17:56,250 --> 00:17:58,125
I'm sure Momo will
get upset with me.

387
00:17:59,291 --> 00:18:02,000
Let me know if you need
anything else, okay?

388
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:03,000
A message.

389
00:18:03,083 --> 00:18:04,000
[SAE]
Huh?

390
00:18:04,083 --> 00:18:05,541
[TOJI]
Last night Momo called me,

391
00:18:05,625 --> 00:18:07,500
but it was right at the time
that my stomach started hurting

392
00:18:07,583 --> 00:18:11,250
so I was barely able to speak,
let alone think straight.

393
00:18:11,333 --> 00:18:12,500
I can't remember what I said

394
00:18:12,583 --> 00:18:15,166
but I'm pretty sure
I hung up on her.

395
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:16,375
Really?

396
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:18,333
[TOJI] So, will you
tell her that I'm sorry

397
00:18:18,416 --> 00:18:19,416
and I didn't mean it?

398
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:21,541
Sure, you got it.
Leave it up to me.

399
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:28,583
Oh, yes. Make-up. I love it.

400
00:18:28,666 --> 00:18:31,166
Goodbye, bruise. Hello, beauty.

401
00:18:33,875 --> 00:18:37,208
[SAE humming]

402
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:48,375
[MOMO] Should I call? I just
want to find out if he's okay.

403
00:18:48,458 --> 00:18:50,666
But what if he thinks
I'm being too pushy?

404
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:57,125
Check it out. It's a card
from everyone in class.

405
00:18:57,208 --> 00:18:58,958
Hey, that's great.

406
00:18:59,041 --> 00:19:00,291
[TOJI laughs, groans]

407
00:19:00,375 --> 00:19:01,750
My stomach hurts when I laugh.

408
00:19:01,833 --> 00:19:03,000
[SAE giggles]

409
00:19:04,125 --> 00:19:06,250
It looks like
Momo didn't sign it.

410
00:19:06,333 --> 00:19:08,083
Huh... That's weird.

411
00:19:08,166 --> 00:19:10,541
You know, I invited her
with me to come visit you.

412
00:19:11,625 --> 00:19:13,041
I see.

413
00:19:13,125 --> 00:19:14,250
[SAE]
I'm sorry.

414
00:19:14,333 --> 00:19:15,541
Ever since I tried to help,

415
00:19:15,625 --> 00:19:18,083
your relationship with Momo
has gone downhill.

416
00:19:18,166 --> 00:19:19,333
Don't be silly.

417
00:19:19,416 --> 00:19:21,750
It'd be best if I didn't
come back here anymore.

418
00:19:22,791 --> 00:19:24,208
Goodbye.

419
00:19:24,291 --> 00:19:25,708
Sae, hold on!

420
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,875
[KAIRI]
What's up with, Toji?

421
00:19:31,958 --> 00:19:34,416
[MOMO] He's been absent for
three straight days now

422
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:36,083
and every time I ask
his friends about him,

423
00:19:36,166 --> 00:19:38,416
they all claim not to
know what's going on.

424
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:40,166
[KAIRI]
Hmm... that's strange.

425
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:41,291
And speaking of strange,

426
00:19:41,375 --> 00:19:43,625
my entire class has
been acting weird.

427
00:19:43,708 --> 00:19:45,750
They keep talking behind my back
and when I look at them,

428
00:19:45,833 --> 00:19:47,708
they either turn away
or stare me down.

429
00:19:47,791 --> 00:19:50,250
Are you being ostracized from
the class or something?

430
00:19:50,333 --> 00:19:51,916
Well... maybe...

431
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,458
[laughs]

432
00:19:53,541 --> 00:19:54,333
[bell chimes]

433
00:19:54,416 --> 00:19:55,708
Oh, great.

434
00:19:57,291 --> 00:20:00,166
Yay. I get to face all the
people that secretly hate me.

435
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:02,166
Find me in the halls if
you get another break today.

436
00:20:02,250 --> 00:20:03,916
I always have a good time
hanging out with you.

437
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:06,291
Yeah, right. If I do that, then
all of your friends will start

438
00:20:06,375 --> 00:20:07,208
spreading more rumors about me.

439
00:20:07,291 --> 00:20:08,125
Come on.

440
00:20:08,208 --> 00:20:09,041
[MOMO yelps]

441
00:20:09,125 --> 00:20:09,708
--[KAIRI gasps]
--[MOMO yelps]

442
00:20:09,791 --> 00:20:12,458
[BOTH yelp]

443
00:20:12,541 --> 00:20:14,666
[KAIRI grunting]

444
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,583
[KAIRI groaning]

445
00:20:16,666 --> 00:20:18,291
[MOMO]
Kairi!

446
00:20:18,375 --> 00:20:20,875
Kairi! Are you okay?

447
00:20:20,958 --> 00:20:22,666
Wow, that hurt... What happened?

448
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:25,125
I'm so sorry...
I slipped on the stairs.

449
00:20:25,208 --> 00:20:27,666
What? Come on, Momo.
You know you pushed me.

450
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:29,083
[MOMO]
No, I did not!

451
00:20:29,166 --> 00:20:31,250
No matter how detestable
I find you and your dirty mind,

452
00:20:31,333 --> 00:20:33,791
I would never try to push
someone down a flight of stairs.

453
00:20:33,875 --> 00:20:35,791
[KAIRI] That sure is
a funny way of putting it.

454
00:20:35,875 --> 00:20:37,958
Can you stand up?

455
00:20:38,041 --> 00:20:39,166
[KAIRI]
I think so.

456
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:44,625
You sure you're okay?

457
00:20:44,708 --> 00:20:46,000
[MOMO gasps]

458
00:20:46,083 --> 00:20:48,000
