You're just so cuddly.

460
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,083
Let go of me,
you filthy pervert!

461
00:20:52,166 --> 00:20:54,000
Ugh! If you keep
pulling this crap,

462
00:20:54,083 --> 00:20:56,333
people are gonna spread
more rumors about me!

463
00:20:56,416 --> 00:20:58,583
Get off! Uh...

464
00:21:01,791 --> 00:21:03,333
[SAE snickers]

465
00:21:04,708 --> 00:21:05,750
[NORI]
What's wrong with you, Kairi?

466
00:21:05,833 --> 00:21:07,750
