[TOJI]
I don't believe it.

484
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,958
Momo! Wait for me!

485
00:21:47,041 --> 00:21:48,708
Stay away from me!

486
00:21:48,791 --> 00:21:50,333
You and I have nothing
to talk about,

487
00:21:50,416 --> 00:21:53,541
so leave me alone before
I do something you'll regret.

488
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:55,583
[KAIRI] Toji's in the hospital
with appendicitis.

489
00:21:55,666 --> 00:21:56,625
[MOMO gasps]

490
00:21:58,208 --> 00:22:00,291
I think Sae's tried to
keep it a secret from you.

491
00:22:01,458 --> 00:22:02,958
[KAIRI] Apparently she
spread word around

492
00:22:03,041 --> 00:22:05,000
